<speech>
Sinestra has struck again! One of her servants,
Tormuk the Necromancer, cast a spell upon two
of Queen Terrellia’s bodyguards, the finest
Elven Archers in the kingdom. The Archers now
fight alongside Tormuk. The Queen wants you to
find the Archers. Once they are alone with you,
the spell will be broken. Scouts say that
Tormuk’s base is in an old castle south of the
Elven lands. Enter the castle through the iron
door and leave through the wooden exit door.
</speech>
<note>A  The first Hero to search for treasure in this room finds 2 Potions
of Healing in the cupboard. Each potion restores up to 4 lost
Body Points.</note>
<note>B  Each chest in this room has a trap on it. If a Hero searches for
